    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnatjone Domini millesimo nonagesimo octavo,
                        anno quartodetjmo <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/4301"
                            >Clementis</persName> pape et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/77">Henritj</persName> inperatoris, die secundo mensis
                        martji, inditjone sexta, <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Houses #Landed_possessions #Walls #Roads"
                            ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>. Quia petimus a vobis in Dei
                        nomine <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Heinricus"
                            >Henrico</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monacho</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposea</placeName>
                        </orgName>, ad confirmandum domno <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1599"
                            >Geronimo</persName> gr(atj)a Dei <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>, uti
                        nobis in Christi nomine <persName><name ref="Iohannes Canavarius"/>Iohanni
                            Canavario</persName> et <persName><name ref="Itrunda"
                            >Itrunde</name></persName> iugalibus seu filiis nostris − et qualis ex
                        nobis obierit sine filiis, eius portjo cadat alteri qui supravixerit − <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellario nomine</rs> concedisti
                        nobis rem iuris vestri monasterii, idest unum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >spatjum terre</rs> ad <rs key="#Houses">mansionem</rs> fatjendam,
                        positum iuxta <rs key="#Walls">murum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">tjvitatis</rs>: a <rs key="#Confinia">primo latere</rs>
                        predicto muro, a secundo latere iure vestri monasterii, a tertjo <rs
                            key="#Roads">via</rs> que pergit sub gatulo vestro, cum portjone ripe
                            <rs key="#Rivers">fluminis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/3558">Teguriensis</placeName>.
                        Habendum, tenendum, supersedendum et in omnibus meliorandum, in annis
                        advenientibus XX et novem ad renovandum; sub pensione quam vobis et vestris
                        successoribus dare debeamus pro predicto spatjo terre, omni martjo mense aut
                        infra inditjonem, <rs key="#Rent_in_money">den(arios) Ven(eticos)
                            duodetjm</rs> et in Natale unam <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">spallam</rs>. Et
                        non liceat nobis predictam rem alicui concedere per aliquam alienatjonem
                        neque in comendatjone mittere. Pro eo quia exinde accepistis, caltjarii
                        nomine, den(ariorum) Ven(eticorum) sol(idos) XX; sub poene nomine <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri untja unam</rs> et soluta poena maneat firmus.</ab>
